description:
The following query fails on Virtuoso 07.20.3217 (tested e.g. against https://linkeddata1.calcul.u-psud.fr/sparql) and 07.20.3230 (tested e.g. against https://dbpedia.org/sparql):
SELECT DISTINCT ( MIN( ?lc ) AS ?l ) ( MIN( ?dc ) AS ?d ) ?s

WHERE {
	{ <http://yago-knowledge.org/resource/wikicat_Alkaloids> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#subClassOf>+ ?s . }
	UNION
	{ <http://yago-knowledge.org/resource/wikicat_Alkaloids> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type>/<http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#subClassOf>* ?s . }
        FILTER EXISTS {
		{ ?s <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#Class> . }
		UNION
		{ [ ] <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#subClassOf> ?s . }
		UNION
		{ ?s <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#subClassOf> [ ] . }
	}
        OPTIONAL { ?pLabel <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#subPropertyOf>* <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> . }
        OPTIONAL { { ?s ?pLabel ?lc . FILTER ( LANGMATCHES( LANG( ?lc ), "en" ) ) } UNION { ?s ?pLabel ?lc . } }
        OPTIONAL { { ?s <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> ?dc . FILTER ( LANGMATCHES( LANG( ?dc ), "en" ) ) } UNION { ?s <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> ?dc . } }
}
GROUP BY ?s
LIMIT 1000

Error message:
Virtuoso S0022 Error SQ200: No column s_0_68-c37.s

However, it starts working under the following circumstances:
Remove feature path wildcards:
SELECT DISTINCT ( MIN( ?lc ) AS ?l ) ( MIN( ?dc ) AS ?d ) ?s

WHERE {
	{ <http://yago-knowledge.org/resource/wikicat_Alkaloids> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#subClassOf> ?s . }
	UNION
	{ <http://yago-knowledge.org/resource/wikicat_Alkaloids> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type>/<http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#subClassOf> ?s . }
        FILTER EXISTS {
		{ ?s <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#Class> . }
		UNION
		{ [ ] <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#subClassOf> ?s . }
		UNION
		{ ?s <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#subClassOf> [ ] . }
	}
        OPTIONAL { ?pLabel <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#subPropertyOf>* <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> . }
        OPTIONAL { { ?s ?pLabel ?lc . FILTER ( LANGMATCHES( LANG( ?lc ), "en" ) ) } UNION { ?s ?pLabel ?lc . } }
        OPTIONAL { { ?s <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> ?dc . FILTER ( LANGMATCHES( LANG( ?dc ), "en" ) ) } UNION { ?s <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> ?dc . } }
}
GROUP BY ?s
LIMIT 1000

Remove OPTIONALs
